Cheferize : A Ruby library to 'translate' strings into Swedish Chef.
Copyright 2010 by Alex Dean.

Usage:
>> class String; include Cheferize; end 
>> "This is a test!".to_chef
=> "Tees is e test, bork bork bork!"

